#. (itstool) path: sect3/para
#: C/index.docbook:1769
msgid ""
"For example, if GNOME is distributed with GOK as the default on-screen "
"keyboard, then this could be replaced with a different program if desired. "
"To replace GOK with the on-screen keyboard application \"onboard\" and "
"additionally activate the assistive tool \"mousetweaks\" for dwelling "
"support, then the following configuration is needed."
msgstr ""
"На пример, ако се ГНОМ испоручује са ГОК-ом као подразумеваном тастатуром на "
"екрану, онда се он може заменити другим програмом ако се жели. Да бисте "
"заменили ГОК програмом тастатуре на екрану „onboard“ и додатно активирали "
"алат за испомоћ „mousetweaks“ за подршку задржавања, потребна су следећа "
"подешавања."

#. (itstool) path: sect3/para
#: C/index.docbook:1777
msgid ""
"Create a desktop file for onboard and a second one for mousetweaks; for "
"example, onboard.desktop and mousetweaks.desktop. These files must be placed "
"in the GDM autostart directory and be in the format as explained in the "
"\"Autostart Configuration\" section of this document."
msgstr ""
"Направите датотеку радне површи за onboard и другу за mousetweaks; на "
"пример, onboard.desktop и mousetweaks.desktop. Ове датотеке морају бити "
"постављене у ГДМ директоријум за самопокретање и бити у формату објашњеном у "
"одељку „Подешавање самопокретања“ овог документа."

#. (itstool) path: sect3/para
#: C/index.docbook:1785
msgid "The following is an example <filename>onboard.desktop</filename> file:"
msgstr "Следи пример <filename>onboard.desktop</filename> датотеке:"

#. (itstool) path: sect3/screen
#: C/index.docbook:1789
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"\n"
"[Desktop Entry]\n"
"Encoding=UTF-8\n"
"Name=Onboard Onscreen Keyboard\n"
"Comment=Use an on-screen keyboard\n"
"TryExec=onboard\n"
"Exec=onboard --size 500x180 -x 20 -y 10\n"
"Terminal=false\n"
"Type=Application\n"
"StartupNotify=true\n"
"Categories=GNOME;GTK;Accessibility;\n"
"AutostartCondition=GNOME /desktop/gnome/applications/at/screen_keyboard_enabled\n"
msgstr ""
"\n"
"[Desktop Entry]\n"
"Encoding=UTF-8\n"
"Name=Onboard Onscreen Keyboard\n"
"Comment=Use an on-screen keyboard\n"
"TryExec=onboard\n"
"Exec=onboard --size 500x180 -x 20 -y 10\n"
"Terminal=false\n"
"Type=Application\n"
"StartupNotify=true\n"
"Categories=GNOME;GTK;Accessibility;\n"
"AutostartCondition=GNOME /desktop/gnome/applications/at/screen_keyboard_enabled\n"

#. (itstool) path: sect3/para
#: C/index.docbook:1803
msgid ""
"The following is an example <filename>mousetweaks.desktop</filename> file:"
msgstr "Следи пример <filename>mousetweaks.desktop</filename> датотеке:"

#. (itstool) path: sect3/screen
#: C/index.docbook:1808
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"\n"
"[Desktop Entry]\n"
"Encoding=UTF-8\n"
"Name=Software Mouse-Clicks\n"
"Comment=Perform clicks by dwelling with the pointer\n"
"TryExec=mousetweaks\n"
"Exec=mousetweaks --enable-dwell -m window -c -x 20 -y 240 \n"
"Terminal=false\n"
"Type=Application\n"
"StartupNotify=true\n"
"Categories=GNOME;GTK;Accessibility;\n"
"AutostartCondition=GNOME /desktop/gnome/applications/at/screen_keyboard_enabled\n"
